  contradictoryClaimId: CL001
  explanationText: "Marcus Vane claims he was with Victor at midnight and left through
    the front door. But his own badge records show he exited at 10:15 PM \u2014 before
    the wall clock stopped at 10:47 PM. The security log then shows his code re-entering
    at 10:51 PM, four minutes after the clock froze. He left, returned, and was present
    when Victor died. His claim of 'midnight' is impossible."
  primaryEvidenceIdA: E001
  primaryEvidenceIdB: E004
